    <abstract>
      <t>In IPv6 networks, performance measurements such as packet loss, delay and jitter of real traffic can be carried out based on the Alternate-Marking method. Usually, the controller needs to collect statistical data on network devices, calculate and present the measurement results. This document proposes a distributed method for on-path flow measurement, which is independent of the controller.</t>
